<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 4: Hollow Victory"</b></font>

22
00:01:43,914 --> 00:01:48,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's always like this when Takumi races.</i></b></font>

23
00:01:48,114 --> 00:01:52,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The tension in the air is the same.</i></b></font>

24
00:01:52,124 --> 00:01:55,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I always give up on him,</i></b></font>

25
00:01:55,494 --> 00:01:57,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but he always wins.</i></b></font>

26
00:02:00,734 --> 00:02:02,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Iketani and Kenji keep saying</i></b></font>

27
00:02:02,734 --> 00:02:06,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that Takumi has no chance against the Lan-Evo.</i></b></font>

28
00:02:06,734 --> 00:02:09,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder if they're right.</i></b></font>

29
00:02:10,404 --> 00:02:12,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He has defeated all the opponents</i></b></font>

30
00:02:12,774 --> 00:02:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that everyone thought he couldn't beat.</i></b></font>

31
00:02:18,444 --> 00:02:21,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't base it on facts, but...</i></b></font>

32
00:02:21,284 --> 00:02:24,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...I think he may beat the Evo IV, too.</i></b></font>

33
00:02:31,094 --> 00:02:35,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't know why, but I'm</i>
<i>suddenly feeling hopeful.</i></b></font>

34
00:02:35,594 --> 00:02:38,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Right, Takumi?</i></b></font>

35
00:03:01,054 --> 00:03:04,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I never thought an Eight-Six</i>
<i>could race this well.</i></b></font>

36
00:03:04,394 --> 00:03:07,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The downhill battle is so deep.</i></b></font>

37
00:03:08,994 --> 00:03:11,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So fast...</i></b></font>

38
00:03:11,004 --> 00:03:13,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What a fast car that is!</i></b></font>

39
00:03:18,074 --> 00:03:22,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just don't understand one thing, Keisuke.</b></font>

40
00:03:22,244 --> 00:03:24,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

41
00:03:24,114 --> 00:03:27,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if he sticks like super glue,</b></font>

42
00:03:27,454 --> 00:03:31,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>how can he pass the Evo IV
with his inferior Eight-Six?</b></font>

43
00:03:31,784 --> 00:03:35,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand that downhill
minimizes the power difference,</b></font>

44
00:03:35,794 --> 00:03:40,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it can never make
the Eight-Six more powerful.</b></font>

45
00:03:40,294 --> 00:03:42,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's slower on the straightaways,</b></font>

46
00:03:42,464 --> 00:03:45,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and since they're equally skilled,
it's almost impossible</b></font>

47
00:03:45,564 --> 00:03:48,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for him to get ahead at a corner.</b></font>

48
00:03:48,034 --> 00:03:50,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he can't get ahead, he'll lose.</b></font>

49
00:03:52,304 --> 00:03:56,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just wait. I don't need to explain it.</b></font>

50
00:03:56,044 --> 00:04:00,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's about to happen right there
is the answer to your question.</b></font>

51
00:04:02,884 --> 00:04:04,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't get it.</i></b></font>

52
00:04:04,484 --> 00:04:06,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He can't get ahead.</i></b></font>

53
00:04:06,824 --> 00:04:08,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's impossible!</i></b></font>

54
00:04:18,834 --> 00:04:22,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He shortens the gap right</i>
<i>before we enter each corner.</i></b></font>

55
00:04:22,334 --> 00:04:26,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But it's partly because my front</i>
<i>tires have lost some pressure.</i></b></font>

56
00:04:29,844 --> 00:04:31,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's an Eight-Six, after all.</i></b></font>

57
00:04:31,614 --> 00:04:33,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It has slow acceleration.</i></b></font>

58
00:04:33,954 --> 00:04:37,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can always pull away after a turn.</i></b></font>

59
00:04:37,284 --> 00:04:40,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It pays to be in front, Kyoichi.</i></b></font>

60
00:04:40,054 --> 00:04:43,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Unless I make a stupid mistake, this race is...</i></b></font>

61
00:04:43,524 --> 00:04:45,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>... 100% mine.</i></b></font>

62
00:04:48,034 --> 00:04:49,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's fast.</i></b></font>

63
00:04:49,364 --> 00:04:51,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's the fastest I've seen,</i></b></font>

64
00:04:51,704 --> 00:04:54,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>as far as acceleration after a turn is concerned.</i></b></font>

65
00:04:59,644 --> 00:05:02,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't stick with him. He has too much power.</i></b></font>

66
00:05:02,974 --> 00:05:05,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never felt this way before.</i></b></font>

67
00:05:18,594 --> 00:05:22,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even with the "ditch" turn, I'm falling behind.</i></b></font>

68
00:05:22,094 --> 00:05:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To offset my slow acceleration,</i></b></font>

69
00:05:24,504 --> 00:05:28,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to exit corners at a much</i>
<i>higher speed than he does.</i></b></font>

70
00:05:28,674 --> 00:05:32,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Then I can catch him before the next corner.</i></b></font>

71
00:05:32,704 --> 00:05:37,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess I have to do what I did</i>
<i>against Ryosuke Takahashi.</i></b></font>

72
00:05:37,014 --> 00:05:39,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Ditch Turn No. 2...</i></b></font>

73
00:05:39,114 --> 00:05:41,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...for faster exit acceleration.</i></b></font>

74
00:05:41,584 --> 00:05:45,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The corner before the bridge is the place.</i></b></font>

75
00:05:45,124 --> 00:05:50,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Can I catch the ditch correctly</i>
<i>if I charge in at top speed?</i></b></font>

76
00:05:50,124 --> 00:05:51,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have one chance!</i></b></font>

77
00:05:53,294 --> 00:05:56,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm different tonight.</i></b></font>

78
00:05:59,134 --> 00:06:01,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're close!</b></font>

79
00:06:01,074 --> 00:06:04,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're just around the corner.</b></font>

80
00:06:04,574 --> 00:06:06,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Honestly...</i></b></font>

81
00:06:06,374 --> 00:06:11,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...I'm not 100% sure if he</i>
<i>can actually pass the Evo IV.</i></b></font>

82
00:06:11,384 --> 00:06:13,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just want to believe</i>
<i>that no one can beat him...</i></b></font>

83
00:06:13,484 --> 00:06:17,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...when my brother couldn't.</i></b></font>

84
00:06:17,554 --> 00:06:19,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't lose!</i></b></font>

85
00:06:19,384 --> 00:06:24,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't forgive you if you lose</i>
<i>to anyone before our rematch.</i></b></font>

86
00:06:26,924 --> 00:06:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is behind!</b></font>

87
00:06:36,074 --> 00:06:37,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now!</i></b></font>

88
00:06:46,844 --> 00:06:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won! This is the end.</i></b></font>

89
00:06:51,354 --> 00:06:53,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He disappeared.</i></b></font>

90
00:06:57,624 --> 00:07:00,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck?!</b></font>

91
00:07:00,294 --> 00:07:04,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He caught the Evo IV at the turn's exit.</b></font>

92
00:07:04,404 --> 00:07:06,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened?!</b></font>

93
00:07:08,734 --> 00:07:10,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's over.</b></font>

94
00:07:12,244 --> 00:07:14,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He got inside.</i></b></font>

95
00:07:18,184 --> 00:07:23,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How?! It's just an old junker,</i>
<i>so how can it be so fast?!</i></b></font>

96
00:07:28,724 --> 00:07:31,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn, I can't control the tires.</i></b></font>

97
00:07:31,224 --> 00:07:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn it!</i></b></font>

98
00:07:37,734 --> 00:07:41,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What an incredible race!
What will happen next?</b></font>

99
00:07:41,934 --> 00:07:45,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing. It's over.</b></font>

100
00:07:45,104 --> 00:07:50,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was over when he moved next
to the Evo IV before this turn.</b></font>

101
00:07:50,274 --> 00:07:53,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way to pass him now.</b></font>

102
00:07:53,214 --> 00:07:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Man, he showed him up big time.</i></b></font>

103
00:07:56,554 --> 00:07:59,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're unreal, Takumi Fujiwara.</i></b></font>

104
00:07:59,684 --> 00:08:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--The Eight-Six is in front!
--He won!</b></font>

105
00:08:02,394 --> 00:08:06,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six has stopped
Team Emperor's sweep!</b></font>

106
00:08:08,834 --> 00:08:12,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable. He beat the Lan-Evo.</b></font>

107
00:08:12,734 --> 00:08:14,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's creepy.</b></font>

108
00:08:26,514 --> 00:08:31,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't feel like I won. Because it's Akina?</i></b></font>

109
00:08:31,554 --> 00:08:33,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I knew exactly where to attack</i></b></font>

110
00:08:33,554 --> 00:08:38,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and when to use the "ditch" turn.</i></b></font>

111
00:08:38,364 --> 00:08:40,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I would've lost anywhere else.</i></b></font>

112
00:08:49,074 --> 00:08:52,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, Kyoichi.</b></font>

113
00:08:52,004 --> 00:08:55,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you have any idea why I'm mad, Seiji?</b></font>

114
00:08:55,844 --> 00:08:58,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you think you can explain</b></font>

115
00:08:58,044 --> 00:09:00,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>why you lost this race?</b></font>

116
00:09:00,854 --> 00:09:04,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I don't. I just couldn't shake him off.</b></font>

117
00:09:04,884 --> 00:09:08,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know how that slow
Eight-Six could keep up with me,</b></font>

118
00:09:08,554 --> 00:09:12,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or what kind of technique he used.</b></font>

119
00:09:12,794 --> 00:09:14,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

120
00:09:14,294 --> 00:09:17,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could you see anything
in the rearview mirror?</b></font>

121
00:09:17,504 --> 00:09:22,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You could've observed
much more from behind.</b></font>

122
00:09:22,004 --> 00:09:25,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Simulation 3" was for that very reason.</b></font>

123
00:09:25,004 --> 00:09:27,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Had you listened to me,</b></font>

124
00:09:27,244 --> 00:09:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you wouldn't have suffered an ugly loss.</b></font>

125
00:09:30,014 --> 00:09:34,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop acting like a stupid monkey
and start using your head!</b></font>

126
00:09:34,854 --> 00:09:36,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I apologize.</b></font>

127
00:09:36,384 --> 00:09:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do we do now, Kyoichi?</b></font>

128
00:09:39,384 --> 00:09:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our plan to sweep Gunma is no more.</b></font>

129
00:09:43,054 --> 00:09:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But regret won't erase this defeat.</b></font>

130
00:09:46,394 --> 00:09:49,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll suck it up and head to Akagi next.</b></font>

131
00:09:49,394 --> 00:09:51,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Red Suns?</b></font>

132
00:09:52,404 --> 00:09:55,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My ultimate target is Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

133
00:09:55,404 --> 00:09:58,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we win in Akagi, I'll be satisfied.</b></font>

134
00:09:58,444 --> 00:10:00,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just have to win.</b></font>

135
00:10:00,674 --> 00:10:03,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about the Eight-Six, Kyoichi?</b></font>

136
00:10:03,674 --> 00:10:07,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have our pride.
We can't just accept the defeat.</b></font>

137
00:10:07,214 --> 00:10:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut up! You don't have to tell me that!</b></font>

138
00:10:12,124 --> 00:10:15,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just leave him to me.</b></font>

139
00:10:15,454 --> 00:10:19,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm the one who is the most upset about this.</i></b></font>

140
00:10:19,724 --> 00:10:22,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was so satisfying last night!</b></font>

141
00:10:22,764 --> 00:10:25,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never felt that satisfied before.</b></font>

142
00:10:25,964 --> 00:10:28,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I remember the Evo IV guy with the ponytail</b></font>

143
00:10:28,304 --> 00:10:30,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>trashed us at the lake by saying,</b></font>

144
00:10:30,644 --> 00:10:34,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"An Eight-Six racer isn't worthy of my time."</b></font>

145
00:10:34,974 --> 00:10:38,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wish I could just rub it in his face.</b></font>

146
00:10:38,214 --> 00:10:41,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right, Takumi? Wasn't it satisfying?</b></font>

147
00:10:41,254 --> 00:10:43,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It wasn't satisfying.</b></font>

148
00:10:43,254 --> 00:10:45,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Why not?</b></font>

149
00:10:45,984 --> 00:10:49,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've had this vague thought lately,</b></font>

150
00:10:49,624 --> 00:10:52,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it became clear last night.</b></font>

151
00:10:52,124 --> 00:10:54,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like racing in Akina.</b></font>

152
00:10:54,494 --> 00:10:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I'm done racing here.
