153
00:10:57,464 --> 00:11:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you think, nothing good comes out of it.</b></font>

154
00:11:00,464 --> 00:11:02,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong with Akina?</b></font>

155
00:11:02,504 --> 00:11:05,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think I won the race last night.</b></font>

156
00:11:05,904 --> 00:11:09,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I actually feel like I lost.</b></font>

157
00:11:09,774 --> 00:11:14,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on, Takumi! Why are you upset?</b></font>

158
