161
00:11:21,594 --> 00:11:24,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've decided to race elsewhere,</b></font>

162
00:11:24,794 --> 00:11:27,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even if it means a defeat.</b></font>

163
00:11:36,104 --> 00:11:37,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Again?</i></b></font>

164
00:11:59,294 --> 00:12:01,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There you are. Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

165
00:12:01,864 --> 00:12:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big news! Akagi will be hot this weekend!</b></font>

166
00:12:05,864 --> 00:12:10,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Team Emperor and the Red Suns are facing off!</b></font>

167
00:12:10,074 --> 00:12:12,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can't miss that!</b></font>

168
00:12:12,704 --> 00:12:15,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rumor has it the guy with the black Lan-Evo</b></font>

169
00:12:15,344 --> 00:12:17,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is racing for Team Emperor.</b></font>

170
00:12:17,214 --> 00:12:21,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi will race for the Red Suns!</b></font>

171
00:12:21,114 --> 00:12:24,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi, are you listening to me?</b></font>

172
00:12:30,424 --> 00:12:32,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! What's the matter, Takumi?</b></font>

173
00:12:32,764 --> 00:12:34,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing.</b></font>

174
00:12:47,914 --> 00:12:51,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When Takumi looks spaced out,</b></font>

175
00:12:51,614 --> 00:12:54,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that means he's thinking
about something, right, Itsuki?</b></font>

176
00:12:54,414 --> 00:12:58,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's actually very rare.</b></font>

177
00:12:58,124 --> 00:13:01,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Most of the time, he's just spaced out</b></font>

178
00:13:01,224 --> 00:13:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and not thinking about anything.</b></font>

179
00:13:03,154 --> 00:13:05,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which one is it today?</b></font>

180
00:13:05,994 --> 00:13:09,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no idea, but he's acting weird today.</b></font>

181
00:13:15,404 --> 00:13:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A black Evo III!
--Is that him?</b></font>

182
00:13:24,714 --> 00:13:27,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--It's him!
--Emperor!</b></font>

183
00:13:35,194 --> 00:13:38,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you come to Akagi?</b></font>

184
00:13:38,194 --> 00:13:40,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come to Akagi and race me.</b></font>

185
00:13:40,934 --> 00:13:42,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A challenge!</b></font>

186
00:13:42,934 --> 00:13:48,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No. But you guys probably don't get it.</b></font>

187
00:13:48,134 --> 00:13:52,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you still remember what
I said to you by the lake?</b></font>

188
00:13:52,574 --> 00:13:54,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're talented,</b></font>

189
00:13:54,104 --> 00:13:56,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you have no chance as
long as you drive an Eight-Six.</b></font>

190
00:13:56,944 --> 00:13:59,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I said.</b></font>

191
00:13:59,484 --> 00:14:02,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can show you what I meant by that.</b></font>

192
00:14:02,314 --> 00:14:06,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you race me, you'll see things
you didn't realize before.</b></font>

193
00:14:06,854 --> 00:14:10,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come to Akagi today or tomorrow, if you like.</b></font>

194
00:14:10,324 --> 00:14:12,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll give you a preliminary race</b></font>

195
00:14:12,324 --> 00:14:14,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>before facing the Red Suns.</b></font>

196
00:14:14,664 --> 00:14:17,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlike the Akina races you're used to,</b></font>

197
00:14:17,164 --> 00:14:20,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it'll be a quick defeat for you.</b></font>

198
00:14:20,164 --> 00:14:24,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in that quick race,
you may learn something new.</b></font>

199
00:14:27,174 --> 00:14:29,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you understand me, come to Akagi.</b></font>

200
00:14:29,774 --> 00:14:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all I wanted to say.</b></font>

201
00:14:39,884 --> 00:14:43,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What nonsense! Who does he think he is?</b></font>

202
00:14:43,224 --> 00:14:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have to go there, Takumi.</b></font>

203
00:14:45,864 --> 00:14:47,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that.</b></font>

204
00:14:47,864 --> 00:14:49,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He acted all cool,</b></font>

205
00:14:49,794 --> 00:14:52,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I bet he just wants revenge in Akagi.</b></font>

206
00:14:52,804 --> 00:14:54,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet he does!</b></font>

207
00:14:54,374 --> 00:14:59,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I've decided not to race in Akina anymore.</b></font>

208
00:14:59,374 --> 00:15:00,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

209
00:15:00,914 --> 00:15:05,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Akagi weren't crowded for
the Emperor-Red Suns challenge,</b></font>

210
00:15:05,144 --> 00:15:08,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I would probably go.
--Takumi!</b></font>

211
00:15:08,054 --> 00:15:12,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate for him to think that
I chickened out, but I'll pass.</b></font>

