00:15:38,944 --> 00:15:40,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

213
00:15:41,784 --> 00:15:43,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw it, Bunta.</b></font>

214
00:15:43,554 --> 00:15:47,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw your son race in Akina.</b></font>

215
00:15:47,624 --> 00:15:50,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Considering how good he already is,</b></font>

216
00:15:50,124 --> 00:15:52,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this engine will be gone soon.</b></font>

217
00:15:52,564 --> 00:15:55,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll be sooner than later.</b></font>

218
00:15:55,064 --> 00:15:56,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you gonna do?</b></font>

219
00:15:56,464 --> 00:16:01,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said you wouldn't
replace it until he lost a race.</b></font>

220
00:16:01,504 --> 00:16:06,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wasn't planning on him lasting this long.</b></font>

221
00:16:06,004 --> 00:16:09,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He just refuses to lose.</b></font>

222
00:16:09,014 --> 00:16:13,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Will the engine blow first, or will he lose first?</b></font>

223
00:16:13,044 --> 00:16:17,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Either way, the new one is ready to go.</b></font>

224
00:16:24,564 --> 00:16:26,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That note...</i></b></font>

225
00:16:30,394 --> 00:16:34,234
