<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She's dating an older man in a Mercedes...</i></b></font>

227
00:16:52,454 --> 00:16:55,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What the hell was that, then?</i></b></font>

228
00:17:01,394 --> 00:17:03,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

229
00:17:08,374 --> 00:17:12,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, there's no way you'll change your mind?</b></font>

230
00:17:12,704 --> 00:17:15,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

231
00:17:15,644 --> 00:17:20,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A family restaurant near Maebashi?</i></b></font>

232
00:17:20,184 --> 00:17:24,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Do you really want me to go? Fine.</i></b></font>

233
00:17:26,324 --> 00:17:29,154
