234
00:17:29,154 --> 00:17:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

235
00:17:37,394 --> 00:17:40,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't get this out of my head.</i></b></font>

236
00:17:40,564 --> 00:17:46,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The more I try to forget it, the more</i>
<i>I think about it and get irritated.</i></b></font>

237
00:17:48,714 --> 00:17:53,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Maybe I like Mogi that much.</i></b></font>

238
00:17:53,614 --> 00:17:55,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So...</i></b></font>

239
00:17:55,384 --> 00:17:59,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...it's silly, but just this once, I'll fall for it.</i></b></font>

240
00:18:08,964 --> 00:18:10,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is it.</i></b></font>

241
00:18:16,904 --> 00:18:19,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A Mercedes.</i></b></font>

242
00:18:32,054 --> 00:18:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Papa, thank you for
understanding my selfishness.</b></font>

